}}"></span>=20
</p><p>The first step to compute its inverse is to create the augmented mat=
rix <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"=
mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><mat=
