r triangular">lower triangular</a> <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki=
/Cholesky_decomposition" title=3D"Cholesky decomposition">Cholesky decompos=
ition</a> of <span class=3D"texhtml"><b>A</b></span>, and <span class=3D"te=
xhtml"><b>L</b>*</span> denotes the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wik=
i/Conjugate_transpose" title=3D"Conjugate transpose">conjugate transpose</a=
> of <span class=3D"texhtml"><b>L</b></span>.
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Analytic_solution">Analytic=
