an efficient way to calculate the inverse of <i>small</i> matrices, but the=
 <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Recursion" title=3D"Recursion">re=
cursive</a> method is inefficient for large matrices. To determine the inve=
rse, we calculate a matrix of cofactors:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
