rix}}}{\begin{pmatrix}\mathbf {C} _{11}&amp;\mathbf {C} _{21}&amp;\cdots &a=
mp;\mathbf {C} _{n1}\\\mathbf {C} _{12}&amp;\mathbf {C} _{22}&amp;\cdots &a=
mp;\mathbf {C} _{n2}\\\vdots &amp;\vdots &amp;\ddots &amp;\vdots \\\mathbf =
{C} _{1n}&amp;\mathbf {C} _{2n}&amp;\cdots &amp;\mathbf {C} _{nn}\\\end{pma=
trix}}}">
