e inverse of <b>A</b> with respect to <i>t</i> is given by<sup id=3D"cite_r=
ef-17" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inverti=
ble_matrix#cite_note-17"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>17<span class=
=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
