athbf {A} ^{-1}\mathbf {A} =3D\mathbf {I} }"></span> using the <a href=3D"h=
ttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Product_rule" title=3D"Product rule">product r=
ule</a>, and then solve for the derivative of the inverse of <b>A</b>:
